<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">About Us</h1>
    <p class="lead">We built MyBaseCamp because teams deserve a calmer, more organized way to work.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>We believe in simplicity, clarity, and making work feel less like chaos and more like progress. MyBaseCamp gives teams a shared space to plan, collaborate, and get things done—without the noise.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Why We Exist</h3>
      <p>Too many tools. Too many tabs. Too many pings. We exist to fix that. With MyBaseCamp, everything your team needs is in one place. No more jumping between apps or losing track of what matters.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5 text-center">
    <%= link_to "Try MyBaseCamp", new_user_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
  </div>
</div>
